From c188afb409a62b9bea40f5c400b18f3a4dc0d63a Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Stefan Cristian B." <stefan.cristian+git@rogentos.ro>
Date: Wed, 6 May 2026 23:21:56 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] Introducing Gentoo stagechooser by @TableFlipper9; gentoo
 modules for download and install

* introduced stage3 choosing module
* created boxes to choose mirrors, arches and stage3 archives
* introduced simple warning to new user regarding
  blank mirror, which means default mirror
* error showing for faild fetches or network problems
* introduced corrected gentoo modules to download, verify and install
  gentoo stage3
* introduced USE flag customization via
  /etc/calamares/modules/gentoopkg.conf
* fixed encryption for both OpenRC and SystemD
* moved configuration and installation of stage3
  from Live /run/ session to user-selected partition
* introduced and corrected full luks2, expanding encryption
  to all openrc and systemd stage3 installations
* implemented hashlib for stage3 verification, replacing previous sha512sum
* replaced which with shutil.which for better reliability
* added comments for USE flags changes, and reasoning
  behind them.
* mandated cryptsetup installation in all necessary cases

Signed-off-by: Morovan Mihai <mihaimorovan1@gmail.com>
Signed-off-by: Stefan Cristian B. <stefan.cristian+git@rogentos.ro>
